lead_paragraph: While policy makers noted some weak points in the domestic economy, the central bank appears on course to increase rates later in the year.

headline.print_headline: Fed Keeps Interest Rates Steady and Says Labor Market Is Improving
headline.main: Fed Keeps Rates Steady and Says Labor Market Is Improving

snippet: While policy makers noted some weak points in the domestic economy, the central bank appears on course to increase rates later in the year.
abstract: Federal Reserve keeps interest rates unchanged, saying economy is not prepared for higher rates; does not indicate that increase is imminent.
